conversations_v0.question: Livingston Flooring tracked the number of broken tiles in each shipment it received last year. How many shipments had less than 60 broken tiles?
conversations_v0.answer:
Count all the leaves in the rows with stems 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5.

You counted 11 leaves, which are blue in the stem-and-leaf plot above. 11 shipments had less than 60 broken tiles.
